DURATION:PT20M
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=WE
SUMMARY:Roadwork — ABS + LEGS day
DESCRIPTION:ABS + LEGS workout (5-10 min):\nSquats x20 / Bicycle crunches x20 / Reverse lunges x10 per leg / Leg raises x12 / Glute bridges x20 / Plank 40s — 2-3 rounds.\nAlso: vitamins (with the car key) + water ~80oz = 3 bottles across the day. Brutal-day floor: 20 squats + 10 push-ups (still counts). Log it: https://thecubeographer.github.io/roadwork/
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
TRIGGER:PT0M
DESCRIPTION:Roadwork — ABS + LEGS day
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
