DURATION:PT20M
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=TH
SUMMARY:Roadwork — PUSH day
DESCRIPTION:PUSH workout (5-10 min):\nIncline then decline push-ups x10 each / Diamond push-ups x8 / Pike push-ups x10 — 3 rounds.\nAlso: vitamins (with the car key) + water ~80oz = 3 bottles across the day. Brutal-day floor: 20 squats + 10 push-ups (still counts). Log it: https://thecubeographer.github.io/roadwork/
