DTSTART:20260703T100000
DURATION:PT20M
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=FR
SUMMARY:Roadwork — PULL day
DESCRIPTION:PULL workout (5-10 min):\nTowel or backpack rows x12 / Single-arm towel rows x10 per side / Supermans x15 / Prone Y-T-W raises x8 each — 3 rounds.\nAlso: vitamins (with the car key) + water ~80oz = 3 bottles across the day. Brutal-day floor: 20 squats + 10 push-ups (still counts). Log it: https://thecubeographer.github.io/roadwork/
